    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Beginning at 3rd level, your experience with Asagami Jutsu grows. You gain 1 Vector Evolution of your choice. Your Boon options are detailed at the end of the Clan description. Also, at 11th, and 15th levels you gain additional boons of your choice as shown in the Boon list in the Asagami Evolution Table.</p><p>Additionally, when you gain a level, you can choose one of the boons you know and replace it with another boon that you could learn at that level.</p><img src=\"systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Cheat%20Sheet/HB%20Asagami%20Evolution%20Table.png\" />",
